---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'

const galleryImages = [
  {
    src: '/photoshootings/ayuna/ayuna-01.jpg',
    alt: 'Ayuna at sunrise on the Amalfi Coast',
  },
  {
    src: '/photoshootings/ayuna/ayuna-02.jpg',
    alt: 'Ayuna portrait in Atrani',
  },
  {
    src: '/photoshootings/ayuna/ayuna-03.jpg',
    alt: 'Ayuna by the sea in Atrani',
  },
  {
    src: '/photoshootings/ayuna/ayuna-04.jpg',
    alt: 'Ayuna with morning light in Atrani',
  },
  {
    src: '/photoshootings/ayuna/ayuna-05.jpg',
    alt: 'Ayuna on the Amalfi Coast',
  },
]

const storyImages = [
  {
    src: '/photoshootings/ayuna/ayuna-06.jpg',
    alt: 'Ayuna portrait from the Atrani session',
  },
  {
    src: '/photoshootings/ayuna/ayuna-07.jpg',
    alt: 'Ayuna portrait from the Atrani morning',
  },
]

const circleImages = [
  '/photoshootings/ayuna/ayuna-circle-01.jpg',
  '/photoshootings/ayuna/ayuna-circle-02.jpg',
  '/photoshootings/ayuna/ayuna-circle-03.jpg',
  '/photoshootings/ayuna/ayuna-circle-04.jpg',
  '/photoshootings/ayuna/ayuna-circle-05.jpg',
  '/photoshootings/ayuna/ayuna-circle-06.jpg',
  '/photoshootings/ayuna/ayuna-circle-07.jpg',
  '/photoshootings/ayuna/ayuna-circle-08.jpg',
  '/photoshootings/ayuna/ayuna-circle-09.jpg',
  '/photoshootings/ayuna/ayuna-circle-10.jpg',
]
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Ayuna - Amalfi.Day"
  description="An Atrani sunrise session capturing Ayuna's story through 50 standout frames."
>
  <section class="ayuna-hero">
    <div class="ayuna-hero__media" style={`background-image:url('${galleryImages[0].src}')`}></div>
    <div class="container ayuna-hero__content">
      <div class="ayuna-hero__text">
        <span class="badge">Atrani, August morning</span>
        <h1>Ayuna</h1>
        <p>
          The Amalfi Coast has always had a magnetic allure, drawing in both locals and wanderers
          from afar with its breathtaking beauty. This August morning, as the first rays of the sun
          painted the skies, Atrani bore witness to a special moment - a meeting of art and
          ambition.
        </p>
        <p>
          It was 7 am, just moments after the sun had announced a new day. The world was still,
          save for the rhythmic lull of the waves and the soft click of a camera capturing moments
          destined to be eternal. I, Gregory Day, have been fortunate to call the Amalfi Coast
          home and have dedicated my craft to capturing its essence through my lens. This morning,
          however, wasn't just about the scenic beauty of Atrani. It was about Ayuna.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section ayuna-heading">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>...Her morning elegance</h2>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--flush">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="ayuna-carousel" aria-label="Ayuna photoshoot gallery">
        {galleryImages.map((image, index) => (
          <figure class="ayuna-carousel__item">
            <img src={image.src} alt={image.alt} loading={index === 0 ? 'eager' : 'lazy'} />
          </figure>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="ayuna-story">
        <p>
          Ayuna, with her boundless spirit and dreams in her eyes, approached me to expand her
          photo portfolio. As a model eager to venture into newer horizons, she embodied the fresh
          energy that mirrors the awakening of a new day. Our collaboration was seamless. With
          each frame, we explored different facets of Ayuna's persona, blending them with the
          serene backdrop of Atrani.
        </p>
        <p>
          We experimented - with outfits that ranged from casual to elegant, with lenses that gave
          varied perspectives, and with angles that showcased both Ayuna and Atrani in their best
          light. In the span of a fleeting hour, magic unfurled. Out of the many shots, 50 stood
          out - each telling its own story, each a testament to the symbiosis of the model, the
          location, and the photographer.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--flush">
    <div class="container">
      <figure class="ayuna-full">
        <img src={storyImages[0].src} alt={storyImages[0].alt} loading="lazy" />
      </figure>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="ayuna-story">
        <p>
          What started as a professional photoshoot soon transformed into a journey of discovery.
          As the sun climbed higher, Ayuna's confidence shone brighter, and the pictures resonated
          with her spirit.
        </p>
        <p>
          To the onlooker, it might seem like a regular photoshoot, but for Ayuna and me, it was a
          memoir - one that would remind us of that beautiful August morning in Atrani when dreams
          were captured, one snap at a time.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section--flush">
    <div class="container">
      <figure class="ayuna-full">
        <img src={storyImages[1].src} alt={storyImages[1].alt} loading="lazy" />
      </figure>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="ayuna-cta">
        <div class="ayuna-cta__lottie" aria-hidden="true">
          <lottie-player
            src="https://lottie.host/7a5b564f-f653-43f6-8f7e-c6eff5651504/cBOQaSku7r.json"
            background="transparent"
            speed="1"
            loop
            autoplay
          ></lottie-player>
        </div>
        <div class="ayuna-cta__content">
          <h3>Capture memories that will last a lifetime!</h3>
          <a class="button" href="#leformx-11">Request now</a>
        </div>
        <div class="ayuna-cta__footer">
          <div class="ayuna-avatars" aria-hidden="true">
            {circleImages.map((src) => (
              <img src={src} alt="" loading="lazy" />
            ))}
          </div>
          <div class="ayuna-cta__note">
            <strong>100+</strong>
            <span>Join the happy costumers</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <script is:inline>
    ;(() => {
      if (customElements.get('lottie-player')) return
      const script = document.createElement('script')
      script.src = 'https://unpkg.com/@lottiefiles/lottie-player@latest/dist/lottie-player.js'
      script.defer = true
      document.head.appendChild(script)
    })()
  </script>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .ayuna-hero {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 75vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    color: #ffffff;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .ayuna-hero__media {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    filter: brightness(0.55);
    transform: scale(1.02);
  }

  .ayuna-hero::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(120deg, rgba(7, 10, 16, 0.8), rgba(7, 10, 16, 0.2));
  }

  .ayuna-hero__content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
  }

  .ayuna-hero__text {
    max-width: 640px;
  }

  .ayuna-hero__text h1 {
    font-size: clamp(2.6rem, 5vw, 4.4rem);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .ayuna-hero__text p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.82);
  }

  .ayuna-heading {
    padding: 2.5rem 0 1rem;
  }

  .ayuna-heading h2 {
    color: #ff7f00;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.8vw, 3.1rem);
  }

  .section--flush {
    padding-top: 0;
  }

  .ayuna-carousel {
    display: grid;
    grid-auto-flow: column;
    grid-auto-columns: minmax(240px, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
    overflow-x: auto;
    padding-bottom: 1rem;
    scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;
  }

  .ayuna-carousel__item {
    margin: 0;
    scroll-snap-align: center;
    border-radius: 18px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-soft);
  }

  .ayuna-carousel__item img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    display: block;
  }

  .ayuna-story {
    max-width: 760px;
  }

  .ayuna-full {
    margin: 0;
    border-radius: 24px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lift);
  }

  .ayuna-full img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
  }

  .ayuna-cta {
    background: var(--color-card);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lift);
    display: grid;
    gap: 2rem;
    justify-items: center;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .ayuna-cta__lottie {
    width: 96px;
    height: 96px;
  }

  .ayuna-cta__lottie lottie-player {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
  }

  .ayuna-cta__content h3 {
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3vw, 2.4rem);
  }

  .ayuna-cta__footer {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .ayuna-avatars {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .ayuna-avatars img {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    border-radius: 999px;
    border: 2px solid var(--color-bg);
    object-fit: cover;
    margin-left: -12px;
  }

  .ayuna-avatars img:first-child {
    margin-left: 0;
  }

  .ayuna-cta__note {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.2rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .ayuna-cta__note strong {
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .ayuna-hero {
      min-height: 70vh;
    }

    .ayuna-carousel {
      grid-auto-columns: minmax(70vw, 1fr);
    }
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
    .ayuna-hero__media {
      transform: none;
    }
  }
</style>
